From Fred Gilham Subject Re Prophetic Warning to New York City Regarding David Wilkerson's While I'm not real sure of his credibility I do remember a book he wrote called A VISION or something like He made a prediction that people who bought gold would be hurt At the time gold was up to about now it is less than half This prediction stuck in my mind because a lot of people where I worked were buying The problem is we tend to remember predictions that come true and forget ones that didn't a la Jean Dixon Does anyone know if there any of his predictions perhaps from the book I mentioned that can pretty definitely be said to have not come true Fred Gilham Peace is only better than war when it's not hell War being hell makes Walker Percy THE SECOND COMING